    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "732182_1_0-13",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "0-13",
      "markText": "阿伦德尔小姐死于五月一日。",
      "totalCount": 384,
      "appLink": "",
      "webLink": ""
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "732182_1_2193-2248",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "2193-2248",
      "markText": "它知道自己绝对不能和顾客的狗打架，但允许自己用声音巧妙地暗示对手，要是没人管着，它会把对方打成怎样的一堆肉酱。",
      "totalCount": 288,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=732182&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=2193&rangeEnd=2248",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/376323905b2c163768ffdec?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=2193&rangeEnd=2248"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "732182_38_2503-2566",
      "chapterUid": 38,
      "range": "2503-2566",
      "markText": "“明天！有时候，波洛先生，明天离现在格外遥远。” “正相反，”波洛答道，“我发现，它总是一成不变地在今天之后到来。”",
      "totalCount": 288,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=732182&chapterUid=38&rangeStart=2503&rangeEnd=2566",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/376323905b2c163768ffdec?chapterUid=38&rangeStart=2503&rangeEnd=2566"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "732182_9_4184-4273",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "4184-4273",
      "markText": "你不了解这些上了年纪的人在面对死亡时，有一种多么顽强的抗争精神。你们这些年轻人会死是因为你们对活着这件事没有兴趣。任何一个年过七十的人都是一个斗士——一个有意志力继续活下去的人。",
      "totalCount": 253,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=732182&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=4184&rangeEnd=4273",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/376323905b2c163768ffdec?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=4184&rangeEnd=4273"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "732182_1_1482-1494",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "1482-1494",
      "markText": "“她自己铺的床自己睡。”",
      "totalCount": 247,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=732182&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=1482&rangeEnd=1494",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/376323905b2c163768ffdec?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=1482&rangeEnd=1494"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "732182_8_1046-1064",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "1046-1064",
      "markText": "侍者端上来两杯被叫做咖啡的可疑液体。",
      "totalCount": 238,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=732182&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=1046&rangeEnd=1064",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/376323905b2c163768ffdec?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=1046&rangeEnd=1064"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "732182_38_2083-2141",
      "chapterUid": 38,
      "range": "2083-2141",
      "markText": "黑斯廷斯上尉？我是塔尼奥斯夫人。请你告诉波洛先生，他完全正确。如果他明早十点能到我这里来，我会把他想要的东西给他。”",
      "totalCount": 238,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=732182&chapterUid=38&rangeStart=2083&rangeEnd=2141",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/376323905b2c163768ffdec?chapterUid=38&rangeStart=2083&rangeEnd=2141"
    },
